{"tid":15980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地產經紀爭客　街頭群毆","createTime":"2016-12-01T08:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T09:04:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0359e8ac89144cf632d496a4c21ac91352784cd","tid":15980,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:57:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161201/19851447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161201%2F19851447&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=3b9dc9b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161201%2F19851447&h=60a438a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161201/19851447</a><br />\n<br />\n地產經紀爭客　街頭群毆<br />\n<br />\n46,803<br />\nInitial ImagePlay Button Image<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n ■一名地產代理昨在大角嘴街頭遭圍毆。讀者提供片段<br />\n■一名地產代理昨在大角嘴街頭遭圍毆。讀者提供片段<br />\n【本報訊】大角嘴浪澄灣本周六重推貨尾單位，十多名地產代理昨午在浪澄灣對開街頭疑為爭客打架，有人手持武器追打，警員接報到場，參與毆鬥者已逃去，遺下一名被打傷後腦的男地產代理，傷者涉公眾地方打架被捕。<br />\n恒隆事後稱若證實事件與參與浪澄灣銷售的地產代理有關，會禁止該代理參與餘下銷售活動，亦會向有關地產代理行發警告信。<br />\n受傷地產代理20歲姓陳，報稱被硬物襲擊。現場為大角嘴海輝道浪澄灣對開街頭。昨午4時許，有市民途經發現十多名穿西裝上衣男子在街頭毆鬥，即用手機拍下經過。從片段所見，參與打鬥者，有單挑有群毆，亦有人手持武器追打對方，雙方拳來腳往，有人被按在地上狂毆，場面混亂，途人見狀走避。有巡警經過查看，打架者即四散，只剩頭部受傷姓陳男子，警員召救護車將他送院，並調查事件。<br />\n■記者黃祺文  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n舖王波叔斥6,300萬買鬼屋之首<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n補習天王谷學生成績差罰錢　家長質疑濫收費職員稱純屬靠嚇"},{"pid":"b953f83cb44a185e0ade9f06b6d640d34da60767","tid":15980,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20161201/org/1480536652_5464.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20161201%2Forg%2F1480536652_5464.jpg&h=99fdea57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07f66c969e5b0b3145e7de94868d19ded867dcb7","tid":15980,"uid":32716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:59:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">傷者涉公眾地方打架被捕</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d47dc6bf9a7ce14770bf77a45bf17781ef16bf","tid":15980,"uid":1134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:02:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">傷者涉公眾地方打架被捕</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依個好笑！"},{"pid":"fc53b7ee17f40fedbbb4f37ed2073aa3021f6b43","tid":15980,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:04:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">傷者涉公眾地方打架被捕</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依個好笑！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鬼叫你唔夠人打咩 當交學費啦"}]}